dct_title_s: Geographers' A-Z street plan of Folkestone and Hythe.
dct_description_sm: Geographers' A-Z Map Co. Ltd. Alternate title: Folkestone & Hythe town plan. With street index. Based upon the Ordnance Survey 1:10.560 maps with the sanction of the Controller of Her Majesty's Stationery Office. Black and white map. Verso: Geographers' A-Z street plan of Dover (1:15,840); Geographers' A-Z street plan of Deal (1:15,840).
